Package: mefa
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate count data handling in ecology and biogeography
Version: 2.0-0
Date: 2008-09-20
Author: Peter Solymos
Maintainer: Peter Solymos <solymos@ualberta.ca>
Description: Object classes for long (database style) and wide (crosstabulated) representations of count data coded by sample, taxon and segment (ie. gender, life stage, sampling period) names. Supports easy processing of the count table along with relational data tables for samples and taxa. Methods are provided for substraction, aggregation, conversion, plotting, summary and reporting. Reports can be generated in plain text or LaTeX format.
License: GPL-2
URL: http://mefa.r-forge.r-project.org/
LazyLoad: yes
